---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Privacy Policy | AstroSignal" description="Privacy Policy for AstroSignal" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <article>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last updated: May 17, 2026</strong></p>
        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how AstroSignal collects, uses, and shares information when you visit astrotobby.site.</p>
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect minimal data. Basic analytics including pages visited and general geographic region may be collected. We do not collect your name, email, or personal details unless you contact us directly.</p>
        <h2>Analytics</h2>
        <p>This site may use privacy-respecting analytics tools to understand traffic patterns and improve content. No personally identifiable information is stored.</p>
        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>This site uses minimal cookies necessary for basic functionality. We do not use tracking cookies for advertising purposes.</p>
        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>AstroSignal contains links to third-party websites including AI tools and platforms. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites.</p>
        <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>Some links on this site may be affiliate links. We may earn a small commission if you click and make a purchase, at no additional cost to you.</p>
        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>This site is hosted on Cloudflare Workers, which provides industry-standard security.</p>
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to request deletion of any personal data submitted to us. Contact us at <a href="mailto:Chanzeratobias@gmail.com">Chanzeratobias@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
      </article>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>